        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You manipulate the target's emotions, potentially allowing you to control it for a brief instant. The target must attempt a Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> On the target's next turn, it's @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 1} and you partially control it, causing it to take a single action of your choice. If it has actions left, it can act normally.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Controlled]{Controlled} for 1 round.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (7th)</strong> On a failure, the target is Controlled for 1 round. On a critical failure, the target is Controlled for up to 1 minute; it receives a new Will save at the end of each of its turns, and on a success, the spell ends.</p>"
